2018-01-01 21-00-00:
	Title: Playtest 20180102
	Author: Paul Chote
	Content: We are excited to welcome the new year with a new playtest! This pre-release build provides a first look at the next OpenRA release. New features include:\n\n  • An overhauled server browser and multiplayer UI\n  • The complete Harkonnen campaign in D2K\n  • Several AI behaviour and performance improvements\n  • New game options and abilities for custom maps\n  • Further Community-driven balance updates to RA\n  • Fixes for several issues on Windows and macOS\n\nHead to www.openra.net for more information and to download the new playtest and let us know what you think! We hope you enjoy it!
